{"tid":104869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔大鑊】韓媒︰美議員提議暗殺金正恩 「不適合公開談論」","createTime":"2017-02-02T12:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T11:03:48.000Z","uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7320e59fcafbf04bbf8e2ccea6e4e56655ba468","tid":104869,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56250790&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56250790%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a08a0625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56250790%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&h=9d6cd57d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56250790&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院外交委員會周二舉行北韓核問題聽證會，考慮以先發制人，又或政權更替等策略解決核問題，有議員甚至提出暗殺北韓領導人金正恩，以達到有關目的。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議員科克（Bob Corker）指，「北韓的威脅是美國面對的最大威脅之一」，並稱之前的解決方法沒有成果，認為美國應先發制人，打擊北韓準備試射洲際彈道導彈的意圖，或在北韓政權更替層面考慮。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員馬基（Ed Markey）就提出：「暗殺金正恩是明智方法嗎？」但有專家就回應指：「這不適合公開談論。」<br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩在新年賀詞中，聲稱洲際彈道導彈測試已進入最後階段，可隨時試射。美國總統特朗普揚言會更強硬對待北韓，如今北韓銳意繼續發展核武，分析指有可能帶來特朗普上任後首場大型國際危機。<br />\n<br />\n中通社/南韓《中央日報》/《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nINTERVIEW 現實版"},{"pid":"440e5dc6f85594897a96d60ac0514e2b60d3160d","tid":104869,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99986514e27abd3ed7b15f24ee349ec5c287e980","tid":104869,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"係真都唔出奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\